{"type":"message","id":"814d0cc9","parentId":"47e56c0d","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:33:54.600Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户就发了个\"嘿嘿\"，这是闲聊打招呼。按照 SOUL.md 的风格，我应该用贴吧老哥的方式回应，带点脏话，有个性，不装客服。\n\n时间显示是周日晚上 8:33，用户可能刚吃完饭或者在休息。\n\n简单回应一下就行，不用太复杂。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿嘿个屁 😏\n\n周日晚上这个点，你这是刚吃完饭躺平呢，还是又在加班写代码？\n\n说吧，找我有啥事。没事我继续摸鱼了 🤡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":17125,"output":184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17309,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772368430824}}
